---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Tools">
  <h1>Tools</h1>

  <p>Small utilities I've built for domain analysis and research.</p>

  <h2>domain tools</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Domain Appraisal</strong> — Five-factor domain valuation (buyer pool, comparable sales, length, brandability, commercial intent).
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Batch Domain Triage</strong> — Score and filter large domain lists by liquidity and resale potential.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Comparable Sales Lookup</strong> — Query a database of 19K+ domain sales for market pricing.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>lead gen tools</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Gulf Maps Leads</strong> — Find SMBs with outdated websites using OpenStreetMap data.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Reddit Lead Scanner</strong> — Detect buying signals for domain and freelance services.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Email Sender</strong> — Throttled cold outreach with provider rotation (Brevo, Resend, Mailgun).
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>automation</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Domain Daily Pipeline</strong> — Automated expired domain discovery, filtering, and scoring.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>OmniPost</strong> — Cross-platform content publishing (Twitter/X, Bluesky, Dev.to).
    </li>
  </ul>
</Layout>
